&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/EUR-FLORENCE-CIBREO-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-7614&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/EUR-FLORENCE-CIBREO-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;EUR- FLORENCE- CIBREO- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;60&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;A classic in the Santa Croce neighborhood of Florence since 1979, Ristorante Cibreo has an ambiance of old world elegance and romance while providing gracious service. Chef Fabio Picchi has earned accolades for his traditional but refined Florentine cooking, notably excluding pasta from the menu. While the menu changes often, some of his dishes have become classics and remain on the menu, such as Potato and ricotta Flan with Meat Sauce Ragu; Florentine Terrine of Chicken and Rabbit Liver with Spinach and Parmigiano; Salt Cod Brandade&nbsp;alla Cassi and a lovely Cheesecake with Bitter Orange Marmalade to conclude. Business casual attire.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Cibreo by phone at +39-055-234-11-00 or by email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@cibreo.com&quot;&gt;info@cibreo.com&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: If not able to make your reservation, as a courtesy please cancel by 2pm the day of your reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed, your reservation may be given away if need arises.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment must be made with your Diners Club card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

